<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Go to <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Fixed assets</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Setup</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Depreciation profile</strong>. For a depreciation profile with <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Depreciation method</strong> = Straight line life remaining**, select the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Half year depreciation on additional acquisitions</strong> check box. If this option is switched on, depreciation convention <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/emea-aut-half-year-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Half year (start year)</strong> is implemented for additional acquisitions.</td>
